Using tariffs for political reasons by Trump could be dangerous for whole world, including EU- European Council President Tusk. If US President Donald Trump uses tariffs for political reasons, it could be dangerous for the whole world, including the European Union, Donald Tusk, president of the European Council, told reporters on Saturday. 
